  <brief_title>Study of Capecitabine in Combination With SIR-Spheres in Patients With Advanced Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase I Study of Capecitabine in Combination With SIR-Spheres in Patients With Advanced Cancer</official_title>
