  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is testing the safety of combining the oral chemotherapy drug capecitabine with
      radio-labeled microspheres injected directly into the liver.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients with adequate liver function and performance status in whom liver-directed therapy
      and capecitabine would be appropriate are eligible for this clinical trial.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
