    <arm_group_type>Experimental</arm_group_type>
    <description>Patients receive capecitabine PO twice daily on days 1-14. Treatment repeats every 21 days for at least 2 courses in the absence of disease progression or unacceptable toxicity. Patients undergo SIRT on day 2 and may undergo a second course of SIRT on day 58.</description>
